      "possibleIdentity": "Joan Webster Price (born 1931 in Camden, New Jersey) is an American abstract artist, sculptor, and educator known for her work in printmaking and her innovative \"solar energy sculptures.\" She was active from the late 1960s through the late 1990s and beyond, often collaborating with her husband, Herbert Price.
